PuzzleGame.Util

类 Constant

  • java.lang.Object
    • PuzzleGame.Util.Constant

  • public class Constant
extends java.lang.Object
    Constant stores many static constants, including page size, map tile coordinates xy, etc.
    Function:
    These constants improve code readability, while keeping track of the relative position on the pane prevents so many changes due to a small offset of the map
